a consortium of government, technical, industry and business interests.Why is 
it unique? It was built five miles offshore . 
</P>
<P>
 We can do better. Our oil platforms have shown outstanding stability offshore. 
Orange County and nearby areas have the best technical people and know-how in 
the world. We could end the bickering concerning land overflights and aviation 
