<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE STYLE FILES: THE PAIN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 THE STYLE FILES 
</P>
<P>
 Six Ways of Looking at Fashion 
</P>
<P>
 TODAY: The Pain 
</P>
<P>
 PHOTOGRAPHER: Al Seib 
</P>
<P>
 ART DIRECTOR: Tracy Crowe 
</P>
<P>
 STYLIST: Joanna Dendel 
</P>
<P>
 MODEL: Bess Hubbard, Elite L.A. 
</P>
<P>
 LEOTARD: J. Crew catalogue 
