<HEADLINE>
<P>
METROPOLITAN DIGEST / LOS ANGELES COUNTY NEWS IN BRIEF: LOS ANGELES COUNTY; 
EMERGENCY DRILL PLANNED TONIGHT AT METRO STATION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Los Angeles city and county officials plan to conduct an emergency drill 
tonight at the Metro Center station on 7th Street, which is the site of both 
Blue Line trolley and Red Line subway stations. 
</P>
<P>
 The drill, scheduled for 9:30 p.m., will include police and fire emergency 
crews. Officials said they have planned the drill to make sure all emergency 
services can be handled in a prompt and orderly fashion. 
</P>
</TEXT>
