 About 400 people have been invited to the Titan Pavilion on campus for the 
black-tie-optional celebration, which begins at 6:30 p.m., followed by 
dinner."Vision and Visionaries" is hosted by Cal State Fullerton President 
Milton A. Gordon and his wife, Dr. Margaret Faulwell Gordon. 
</P>
